								Built a number of professional projects, including a Ruby on Rails Portfolio app, an enterprise-level Ruby on Rails Overtime app, and an app for Freelancers written in TypeScript and Angular 2. <br> Each project utilizes a variety of advanced functionality designed to deliver a sleek, user-friendly experience. <br>
