							<span><b>CUNY Lehman College</b> <i>2016-2017</i></span>
							<span class="about-descrip">
								Maintained an above-average GPA while pursuing a Bachelor's in Health Education and Promotion.
								<ul>
									<li>Health Counseling</li>
									<li>Statistical Computation</li>
									<li>Research Methods and Epidemiology</li>
								</ul>
							</span>
						</div>

						<div class="card card-block align-left">
							<span><b>CUNY Bronx Community College</b> <i>2011-2015</i></span>
							<span class="about-descrip">
